    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Plain C++ handle for a server-side VoiceInput (STT) session. Created by <ref refid="class_u_tryll_subsystem" kindref="compound">UTryllSubsystem</ref> after a successful CreateVoiceInputResponse. The Unreal counterpart to the C++ Tryll::VoiceInput and the Unity TryllVoiceInput.</para>
<para>Ownership: typically held as TSharedPtr&lt;FTryllVoiceInput&gt; by UTryllVoiceInputComponent. Lifetime: deterministic — the owning component releases the shared_ptr; this triggers <ref refid="class_u_tryll_subsystem_1a1adc8fdfdac65a29c179f6a589376a88" kindref="member">UTryllSubsystem::RequestDestroyVoiceInput()</ref>.</para>
<para>All callbacks are invoked on the game thread (from UTryllSubsystem::Tick). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
